otprint and the build time – which, impressively, took just over a day for the main frame.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575764\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575764\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Console-House-CLT-Danube-Bend-Hungary-Hello-Wood-6-810x606.jpg\" alt=\"A modern cabin with a metal roof and large windows stands on stilts among dense green trees on a hillside under a clear sky.\" width=\"810\" height=\"606\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Console-House-CLT-Danube-Bend-Hungary-Hello-Wood-6-810x606.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Console-House-CLT-Danube-Bend-Hungary-Hello-Wood-6-800x599.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Console-House-CLT-Danube-Bend-Hungary-Hello-Wood-6-768x575.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Console-House-CLT-Danube-Bend-Hungary-Hello-Wood-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575765\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575765\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Console-House-CLT-Danube-Bend-Hungary-Hello-Wood-7-810x607.jpg\" alt=\"Modern black metal cabin with a covered balcony on stilts, surrounded by dense green trees and vegetation.\" width=\"810\" height=\"607\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Console-House-CLT-Danube-Bend-Hungary-Hello-Wood-7-810x607.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Console-House-CLT-Danube-Bend-Hungary-Hello-Wood-7-800x599.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Console-House-CLT-Danube-Bend-Hungary-Hello-Wood-7-768x575.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Console-House-CLT-Danube-Bend-Hungary-Hello-Wood-7.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw